com.primavera.common.value

Class EndDate

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Date
      • java.sql.Date
        • com.primavera.common.value.EndDate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Comparable<Date>

    public class EndDate
extends Date
    This value type is used to define an end date. It is used for all finish date fields, and is a wrapper class for java.sql.Date.
